Thomas H. Cormen, Charles E. Leiserson, Ronald L. Rivest, and Clifford
Stein.<br> <i>Introduction to Algorithms</i>, Third edition.<br> The
MIT Press, 2009. Translations: French (Dunod, 2010), Italian
(McGraw-Hill/Italy, 2010), German (Oldenbourg Wissenschaftsverlag, in
progress), Polish (Wydawnictwo Naukowe PWN Sp&oacute;lka Akcyjna, in
progress).

