Thomas H. Cormen and Elena Riccio Davidson.<br>
Using FG to Reduce the Effect of Latency in Parallel Programs Running
on Clusters.<br>
To appear in Sanguthevar Rajasekaran and John Reif, editors, <i>CRC
Handbook of Parallel Computing: Models, Algorithms and
Applications</i>, CRC Press.

